  • java.lang.Object
    • webservice.ServicioWebCallbackHandler

  • public abstract class ServicioWebCallbackHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    ServicioWebCallbackHandler Callback class, Users can extend this class and implement their own receiveResult and receiveError methods.
